---
/**
 * /prompt-pack/grazie
 * Pagina di ringraziamento post-acquisto Stripe.
 * Stripe redirige qui dopo checkout completato.
 */
export const prerender = false;
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Acquisto completato — Marco Munich</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bricolage+Grotesque:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --gold: #C58A37;
      --bg: #0C0B09;
      --cream: #F0EBE3;
      --muted: rgba(240,235,227,0.5);
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--cream);
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .icon {
      width: 64px; height: 64px;
      background: rgba(197,138,55,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(197,138,55,0.3);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.15;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    h1 em {
      font-style: normal; color: var(--gold);
    }

    .body {
      font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 42ch;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    }

    .steps {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;
      max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .step {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .step__num {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 28px; height: 28px;
      background: rgba(197,138,55,0.12);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', system-ui, sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .step__text {
      font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;
      color: rgba(240,235,227,0.7);
    }

    .step__text strong {
      color: var(--cream); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .back-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="icon">✓</div>

    <p class="eyebrow">Acquisto completato</p>

    <h1>Il pagamento è andato<br>a <em>buon fine.</em></h1>

    <p class="body">
      Tra pochi secondi ricevi un'email con il link per accedere al tuo Prompt Pack.
      Controlla la casella di posta — anche lo spam, per sicurezza.
    </p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__num">1</div>
        <div class="step__text">
          <strong>Controlla la tua email</strong>
          Trovi un messaggio da <em>noreply@marcomunich.com</em> con il link di accesso.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__num">2</div>
        <div class="step__text">
          <strong>Clicca il link nell'email</strong>
          Il link è personale — aprilo dal dispositivo che preferisci e aggiungilo ai preferiti.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step__num">3</div>
        <div class="step__text">
          <strong>Hai accesso per sempre</strong>
          Il pack è tuo — tutti gli aggiornamenti futuri arrivano allo stesso link, senza costi aggiuntivi.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Torna alla homepage</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
